{"tid":2432151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【元朗721】謝英權大律師質疑證人受外界資訊影響認錯人","createTime":"2021-03-04T06:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:45:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa36925639b780068f686bf26d0383055312a468","tid":2432151,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"謝英權大律師:<br />\n<img src=\"http://admiraltychambers.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/IMG-20170315-WA0000-240x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fadmiraltychambers.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FIMG-20170315-WA0000-240x300.jpg&h=951b37c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721元朗白衣人暴動案今在區域法院續審，由當日途經元朗遇襲的控方證人C繼續作供。辯方質疑C根本沒有在當日見過被告鄧英斌，只是受外界資訊影響才錯認鄧，C否認。<br />\n<br />\n鄧英斌的代表大律師謝英權盤問證人C時，詢問C可否在庭上模仿鄧當日所作出的威嚇動作，C直言：「唔可以，唔想做啲唔正確的動作。」，並稱不肯定是否鄧作出指嚇行為，還是他身邊的人指嚇，只記得鄧當時表情激動。被問到為何確定鄧與其他人為一伙，C解釋：「佢地全部都揸住武器，但冇互相毆鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n謝大律師隨後播放多條C所在車廂內外的錄影片段，要求C在看見鄧時指出來，惟C未能在片段中看見鄧。謝再播出當日受襲車廂對面月台的錄影片段。片段中，有一名疑似鄧的男子手持手機拍攝，謝隨即質疑鄧當日在月台上根本沒有持有任何武器，C回答不知道。謝其後又指C「可能記錯，並非全心誤導警方」，但因好多資料在網上流傳，C可能在網上看到相關的資料，才在認人時指當日在月台上見過鄧，C否認。"},{"pid":"cf9acbf09b08639b95350ed25914a483dee04d87","tid":2432151,"uid":28195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"謝英權用嗰咁既名，奶極都難以上位。<br />\n睇下梁振英就明白，日日係度瘋狂爭紥"},{"pid":"9e46778b7b99233e3e6318380dca633367932b84","tid":2432151,"uid":52779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"嘩, 721都仲夠膽咁嚟?"},{"pid":"aaae8faff1cca63e06cc9a4e3ae0ce2a6aa98e99","tid":2432151,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ca8e347ff63737aff0499ff8bc792516247c7","tid":2432151,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"感謝居英權"},{"pid":"2f3f098c5f1211c9c2cd319eb668f0cb65f4ba7d","tid":2432151,"uid":117301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"謝英權<br />\n感謝英國賦權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367e79e3cd28b127f4e12561f6fe6c18eba87b92","tid":2432151,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9283e93a6861b4d25f1297c300232d51da633019","tid":2432151,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e8130b441103709dc20b12de22bfc7cb73b0e1","tid":2432151,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"依家打程序法...？"},{"pid":"629c3a7a0322d6d7e0e7f5e1c955182b7fdd936b","tid":2432151,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e46778b7b99233e3e6318380dca633367932b84","tid":2432151,"uid":52779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"嘩, 721都仲夠膽咁嚟?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"受人錢財"}]}